http://www.thehindu.com/news/cities/Hyderabad/HDFC%E2%80%99s-property-expo-opens/article14016572.ece

A ‘Ready to Occupy Homes’ exhibition organised by leading housing finance company HDFC and featuring 3,500 properties opened here on Saturday. From apartments to villas, the two-day expo at JRC Conventions and Trade Fairs, Raidurgam, has a range of properties priced from Rs.25 lakh upwards. On Sunday, the exhibition will remain open from 10 a.m. to 7 p.m. Member, Executive Management of HDFC, Mathew Joseph said the speciality about ready to move-in properties is the “comfort of seeing” available for customers.